Sahaja Yogi: Mahargha Punya kaal.

00:11:33.034 --> 00:11:42.563
Mataji: Maharga, you see.

00:11:42.563 --> 00:11:46.458
Just now I told you Maharga Punya Kaal.

00:11:46.458 --> 00:11:49.642
Such a great auspicious day. Nothing to beat Maharga.

00:11:49.642 --> 00:11:58.120
Argha means, Maharga, Argha. Argha means to offer water, to give argha.

00:11:58.120 --> 00:12:00.839
Now you should give water to this land of yours.

00:12:00.839 --> 00:12:03.569
You need rain and all arrangements should be done.

00:12:03.569 --> 00:12:07.374
But, then you should also   deserve it.

00:12:07.374 --> 00:12:10.200
Whether Sahaja Yogis deserve or not, should be seen.

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:14.257
It will be better if without taking many efforts you achieve Sahaja Yoga.

00:12:14.257 --> 00:12:16.783
And whatever gains you can get, you should take.

00:12:16.783 --> 00:12:20.190
Today is a great day. It is Maharga Punya today.

00:12:20.190 --> 00:12:22.052
I had already said earlier.

00:12:22.052 --> 00:12:28.114
So today is a special day. All of you have given me such pleasure and happiness,

00:12:28.114 --> 00:12:31.507
you all came here, took so much trouble,

00:12:31.507 --> 00:12:35.776
I request you all with folded hands  to  take similar  efforts for Sahaja Yoga.
